New in 0.22:
- Scanning for stations can be aborted

New in 0.21:
- FM band selection (requires kernel driver patch)
- forward and backward scanning

New in 0.201:
- experimental (untested) support for FM band selection

New in 0.20:
- FM tuner chip is correctly powered down when closing the device
- current signal strength can be retrieved
- automatic scanning for radio stations has been implemented
